divs: Sighting Detailsi was at home,feeling strange for a few days,compelled to go outside,seen jets flying over then the circular object dropped out of the clouds,hardly any sound,just a low hum,moving very slow,watched it go southwest,then it went back up in the clouds,felt happy,for some reason i knew what i was about to see.
Summary: compelled to go outside,dropped out of the clouds long enough for me to see it ,heading southwest
